          H1FV7 H1DS7 PWITH H3DS18H H3HR23;

          !f8 BY H1TO15* H1TO17 H1TO5 H1TO32 H1TO36 H1TO42;
          !f9 BY H3TO38* H3TO40 H3TO7 H3TO110 H3TO113 H3TO119;
